+### Building
+
+You can build etcd from source:
 
 ```sh
 git clone https://github.com/coreos/etcd
 ./build
 ```
 
+This will generate a binary in the base directory called `./etcd`.
+
+_NOTE_: you need go 1.1+. Please check your installation with
+
+```
+go version
+```
+
